{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":" whose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"text":" property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the value of this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property may be overridden at any time.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The usage of ","type":"text"},{"code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been deprecated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"use the map view’s property ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"},{"text":"instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1610","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol","title":"contentInset","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)contentInset","fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsC